# Paper Digest

A weekly, auto-curated roundup of new papers in **cardiovascular CFD, hemodynamics, and physics-informed ML**. Papers are pulled from OpenAlex and arXiv, classified into one of six research tiers with Claude, and posted here every Monday morning (UTC).

